  "mdSummary": "# Table\n\nMinimal styled HTML table with header, row, cell components.\n\n**Package:** `Lumeo` · **Category:** Data Display/Tables\n**Docs:** https://lumeo.nativ.sh/components/table\n\n## Parameters\n| Owner | Name | Type | Default | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Table | ChildContent | `RenderFragment?` | `` |  |\n| Table | Class | `string?` | `` |  |\n| Table | AdditionalAttributes | `Dictionary<string, object>?` | `` |  |\n| TableBody | ChildContent | `RenderFragment?` | `` |  |\n| TableBody | Class | `string?` | `` |  |\n| TableBody | AdditionalAttributes | `Dictionary<string, object>?` | `` |  |\n| TableCaption | ChildContent | `RenderFragment?` | `` |  |\n| TableCaption | Class | `string?` | `` |  |\n| TableCaption | AdditionalAttributes | `Dictionary<string, object>?` | `` |  |\n| TableCell | ChildContent | `RenderFragment?` | `` |  |\n| TableCell | Class | `string?` | `` |  |\n| TableCell | AdditionalAttributes | `Dictionary<string, object>?` | `` |  |\n| TableHead | ChildContent | `RenderFragment?` | `` |  |\n| TableHead | Class | `string?` | `` |  |\n| TableHead | AdditionalAttributes | `Dictionary<string, object>?` | `` |  |\n| TableHeader | ChildContent | `RenderFragment?` | `` |  |\n| TableHeader | Class | `string?` | `` |  |\n| TableHeader | AdditionalAttributes | `Dictionary<string, object>?` | `` |  |\n| TableRow | ChildContent | `RenderFragment?` | `` |  |\n| TableRow | Class | `string?` | `` |  |\n| TableRow | AdditionalAttributes | `Dictionary<string, object>?` | `` |  |\n\n## Slots\n- `ChildContent` (Table) — RenderFragment slot\n- `ChildContent` (TableBody) — RenderFragment slot\n- `ChildContent` (TableCaption) — RenderFragment slot\n- `ChildContent` (TableCell) — RenderFragment slot\n- `ChildContent` (TableHead) — RenderFragment slot\n- `ChildContent` (TableHeader) — RenderFragment slot\n- `ChildContent` (TableRow) — RenderFragment slot\n\n## Events\n- (none)\n\n## Sub-components\n- `TableBody`, `TableCaption`, `TableCell`, `TableHead`, `TableHeader`, `TableRow`\n\n## Cascading values it expects\n- (none)\n\n## Services it injects\n- (none)\n\n## Keyboard\n—\n\n## Example\n```razor\n<Table />\n```\n\n## CSS variables\n`--color-border`, `--color-muted`, `--color-muted-foreground`\n\n## Files\n- `UI/Table/Table.razor`\n- `UI/Table/TableBody.razor`\n- `UI/Table/TableCaption.razor`\n- `UI/Table/TableCell.razor`\n- `UI/Table/TableHead.razor`\n- `UI/Table/TableHeader.razor`\n- `UI/Table/TableRow.razor`\n"
